nId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7101c586b2","type":"paragraph","text":"列宁——好用重复长句","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c4e131ddd7","type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林——好用相同句代表不同内容，如党史四章（与马平日反）","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7a93df0d84","type":"paragraph","text":"莫噢④——不交代清白：一、本身有不明确处，二、留一手。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1c56309e4b","type":"paragraph","text":"一○一⑤——交代太清楚（失去神秘性）","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dfc0ce5204","type":"paragraph","text":"［注］","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"92aa294212","type":"paragraph","text":"①这是林彪的一次谈话，由叶群亲笔记其要点。据原编者说明、谈话记录时间为1961至64年间。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fb5bd51907","type":"paragraph","text":"②即《费尔巴哈和德国古典哲学的终结》","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a955419e15","type":"paragraph","text":"③“历唯”，好历史唯物主义。“辩唯”，即辩证唯物主义。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3661aac8d0","type":"paragraph","text":"④“莫噢”，指毛泽东。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"54025273c1","type":"paragraph","text":"⑤“一○一”，指林彪。40年代末林已用此代号。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1a7232b9df","type":"paragraph","text":"其二①","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a00f79ac17","type":"paragraph","text":"1970.3.13","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"327644608a","type":"paragraph","text":"哲学语言上，黑②说黑话（指形式上晦涩难懂）马·半黑话（也指语言表达受黑影响）恩带黑话（比马说得清楚些）列爱说冗长话（应大胆找核心）斯语言清楚（思想不稳，如对矛盾、对生力、生关③等）","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"25a4add7e1","type":"paragraph","text":"一号文理通顺，对整个辩法唯论了解（■多问题糊涂有①）。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6dc77f35e7","type":"paragraph","text":"言行相反（言论前后相左，如内矛）","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"99a4d9b7d7","type":"paragraph","text":"别人搞好东西压住，事后归己（合作社□）","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"502595fbd7","type":"paragraph","text":"拗相公（跃时）","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3e00783afd","type":"paragraph","text":"四清⑤","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"10a2d923e0","type":"paragraph","text":"四害⑥","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8d3021cc95","type":"paragraph","text":"百花 形而上","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1e9dcd2199","type":"paragraph","text":"辩不够","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"81a187e562","type":"paragraph","text":"复课","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e6a4157c2b","type":"paragraph","text":"大虎牌（金马问题）","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e933718f4f","type":"paragraph","text":"不关心国民生计。名、位、权利。","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"48258f56af","type":"paragraph","text":"［注］","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"453df831b5","type":"paragraph","text":"①这是叶群记录的林彪谈话。据原编者说明，此件记在《一○一笔记》上。","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"72011113e9","type":"paragraph","text":"②“黑”，指黑格尔。","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ada1e5893d","type":"paragraph","text":"③“生力”，即生产力。“生关”，即生产关系。","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"64a5b39ad7","type":"paragraph","text":"④“一号”，指毛泽东。可参阅第四、六、八则笔记。林彪主张“一是多”“多分二派”，认为毛只说“一分为二”有点简单。","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"293ebc8e5a","type":"paragraph","text":"⑤“四清”，即1964年至65年间全国展开的社会主义教育运动，打击对象是基层单位的“走资本主义道路当权派”。","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"de0ebd6070","type":"paragraph","text":"⑥“四害”，指50年代毛泽东倡弄的“除四害”即消灭鼠、雀、蝇、蚊的大规模活动。","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"94fb19ccf0","type":"paragraph","text":"其三①","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d20feb2136","type":"paragraph","text":"△黑格尔说：何谓伟大人物？","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a8ff2b70c8","type":"paragraph","text":"伟大人物就是公众利益的代表者。","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b7efe2f854","type":"paragraph","text":"△一○一说：何谓当代伟大人物？","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ca861584d9","type":"paragraph","text":"一号利益的代表者（应声虫）。","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"492e662c4f","type":"paragraph","text":"［注］","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b03689b772","type":"paragraph","text":"①这是叶群记录的林彪谈话。据原编者说明，谈话记录时间当在60年代初。","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2a66263d76","type":"paragraph","text":"其四①","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"91159c8759","type":"paragraph","text":"辩证法是两点论（两组成部分）","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c5d55a5020","type":"paragraph","text":"辩证法又是一点论","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3b0ede2d65","type":"paragraph","text":"二者一致性（二合为一）","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ce14e40fb0","type":"paragraph","text":"无一分为二，无矛盾观念","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e470ebd82f","type":"paragraph","text":"无二合为一，无统一观念","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c27671b566","type":"paragraph","text":"（变成康德的辩证法）","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7fcd300fc6","type":"paragraph","text":"对立而不统一","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b18d339b41","type":"paragraph","text":"反对：一、只有统一，不见成份。二、只有成份，未见统一。三、反对不见大成份。","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7071538b5d","type":"paragraph","text":"［注］","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c88fbe895f","type":"paragraph","text":"①这是叶群记录的林彪谈话。据原编者说明谈话记录时间在1961至64年间。","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5d0e77f585","type":"paragraph","text":"其五①","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"318dc8c3ad","type":"paragraph","text":"69，12，1。苏州记","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fe83455c90","type":"paragraph","text":"△姨毫②30年前叫两点论——真善美和假恶丑。","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a569b09f1c","type":"paragraph","text":"一、叫对他真善美，对其他人假恶丑。二，叫对他也是除有真善美的一面，也要有假恶丑的一面。其中有辩证法。","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f0f26d404b","type":"paragraph","text":"△到陕之初，当老巴（原编者注，据‘林办’人员说，叶群常对林立衡、林立果谈话时称林彪为‘老巴’要独立打仗时。他也提出两点论——只有服从，才能独立。意即百依百顺，才能有职有权。提出独立性有余，服从性不足之特点。","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"91b5759f71","type":"paragraph","text":"△提出独到有余，广博不足。","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c520067c64","type":"paragraph","text":"［注］","index":61,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"57c49ab78d","type":"paragraph","text":"①这是叶群记录的林彪谈话。","index":62,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0d295ae061","type":"paragraph","text":"②“姨毫”为“一号” 谐音。","index":63,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"08145c57a3","type":"paragraph","text":"其六①","index":64,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"df64ea196d","type":"paragraph","text":"三不（1）不干扰人之决心（免己负责）","index":65,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f0f5d4be7a","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）不批评（免争领导之嫌）","index":66,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7975c161f9","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）不报坏消息（去影射之嫌）","index":67,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3090b8f869","type":"paragraph","text":"三要要响应","index":68,"publicationId":"GPCR