6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"057675021d","type":"paragraph","text":"△两点论无往不利之体验。","index":145,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fc4468b688","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）现用不着将来用得着（阶段论）","index":146,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"608c8a4285","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）不放心论（心情不放心时）","index":147,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f0dbb73911","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）人们通病只检一点（好检一点，重一点）","index":148,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3bb2f7f304","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）但也有人平均主义（故仍需二点论之立场）","index":149,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c949ea337e","type":"paragraph","text":"（5）不痛快","index":150,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1228522153","type":"paragraph","text":"理论上是辩法，是客观存在，是革命的政治上人们通病：","index":151,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d4810e39c8","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）单打一（提宽放严，提生产放训练）","index":152,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f998646e4f","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）只干不查","index":153,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"92fb77bae5","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）只干不想","index":154,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e1796d2731","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）平均折衷主义","index":155,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"121b777115","type":"paragraph","text":"△参观发现写实的重要——雕螃蟹看蟹雕蟹看花绣花抽象派只凭幻想胡来","index":156,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"97678f2fe9","type":"paragraph","text":"△但个人大局（立场）——明知不是理事急且相随","index":157,