bd639","type":"paragraph","text":"①这一则是林彪亲笔写的，无时间推断应在60年代初。","index":170,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f6b25f1ebd","type":"paragraph","text":"②“刘彭”，当指刘少奇，彭真。","index":171,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7e920be40b","type":"paragraph","text":"其十三①","index":172,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2cec071ddb","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、忍耐、大度的科学根据。","index":173,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"74dcbca545","type":"paragraph","text":"夜梦朱理治②骂我一句，我即全力与之大吵一场。","index":174,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"26334c689f","type":"paragraph","text":"敌人常派出许多小股部队来挑战，以分散、牵制、耽误我的主攻，使我兵力分散，对此我不可分兵或全力展开大战，而应不与纠缠。","index":175,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a9a79237c2","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、以小狗去辱他，或即视若无睹，置之不理。千万记住此理，并反用此法去分散敌人。","index":176,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c1ea079870","type":"paragraph","text":"对事物、主义，对一切侮辱，皆当本此原理对待。","index":177,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"152b3365c0","type":"paragraph","text":"“林立果在此处以小字插写：反对平分兵力，分散兵力，浪费兵力，遇到小敌就斗。集中主力打歼灭战。任何时候不要迷失主攻目标”","index":178,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4cdaabfc19","type":"paragraph","text":"勿上敌牵制队、游击队的当（千百朱理治），社交、处事，共同原理。庐山之彭③、世上之彭甚多。岂可为了区区小人、区区小事，而耽误自己的终身大身！","index":179,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f5381b0768","type":"paragraph","text":"丙、不能亲人的供养、教育不管，使他受苦④。对国、对社会、对人类同一原理。","index":180,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cdfb4a1a43","type":"paragraph","text":"［注］","index":181,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3f41cace90","type":"paragraph","text":"①这一则也是林彪的亲笔。据原编者说明，写在1963年《工作手册》（十）上。小字经原“林办”工作人员辨认，是林立果的笔迹。","index":182,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b63829e002","type":"paragraph","text":"②朱理治，中国共产党建立初期加入的共产党员。他不赞成毛泽东的“五四”运动属于无产阶级领导的观点，认为“五四”是知识分子领导的。","index":183,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"532f626e8d","type":"paragraph","text":"③“彭”，指彭德怀。","index":184,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"657b18e284","type":"paragraph","text":"④此处可能指林彪前妻张梅所生的小琳因叶群不喜欢而在外流浪，不能进京的事。","index":185,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a87cb8019b","type":"paragraph","text":"其十四①","index":186,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6546c9763c","type":"paragraph","text":"1962.01.23","index":187,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9a4082191a","type":"paragraph","text":"睡好觉，身体乃一切之物基。","index":188,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d6bc9609d1","type":"paragraph","text":"一○一人大会堂五级干会报苦经教②：（1）秀才不行，束缚于既成思想词句或目空一切。","index":189,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ff8149942f","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）不怕人多会大（反正有麦克风），只对一二人，对表情亲善者，以增信心。","index":190,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"debc04d302","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）另件箱法③有大效：一深刻，二可以应付任何急活。","index":191,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"36fc25af8f","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）另件逐一列出，再梳成几条辫子，而成一良好报告。","index":192,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"78cf441e66","type":"paragraph","text":"（5）无论任何会，讲任何问题，都需要有典型例子，论点才能立体化，易解，生色——凡例皆大笑。","index":193,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a0706978c5","type":"paragraph","text":"（6）每纸留小半页，用填例子，利用红笔。","index":194,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"107ed7721d","type":"paragraph","text":"（7）原来次序，可于讲话时依自己情绪，听众及首长之不同反应而改换之（如插话、鼓掌、振动）。勿被原次序所束缚。用划勾法免漏。","index":195,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5abb8ea126","type":"paragraph","text":"（8）初稿时应请内行阅，以免差误。","index":196,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f9e3c112d0","type":"paragraph","text":"（9）好辞藻、好知识、历史、好哲理、现代常识总有用，平时应大量积累。","index":197,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eb63d3a775","type":"paragraph","text":"（10）讲时应照顾听众利益，及大首脑（一号、干部辛苦、各脑、周）利益，分别拉之。","index":198,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cacb86f96e","type":"paragraph","text":"（11）长讲话：鼓动放前，先鼓动起劲，把精彩的放前，如电影，才能听下去。短：可放后，以有余味。","index":199,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8f45871b00","type":"paragraph","text":"［注］","index":200,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4299027991","type":"paragraph","text":"①林彪为准备1962年1月29日在五级干部会《七千人大会》上讲话，谈了准备方法和注意要点，这是叶群作的记录。","index":201,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5b6c28c5af","type":"paragraph","text":"②“经教”，经验教训之省略语。","index":202,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a0fa6b658d","type":"paragraph","text":"③“另件箱”，指分类储存的各种语录和材料。","index":203,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"186b44fd1f","type":"paragraph","text":"其十五①","index":204,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"91139ddf2a","type":"paragraph","text":"三级表态：说坏——右","index":205,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7d9d4599c8","type":"paragraph","text":"不说——中","index":206,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a05501b1a3","type":"paragraph","text":"说好——左","index":207,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"705bd42edf","type":"paragraph","text":"［注］","index":208,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"881fb73d95","type":"paragraph","text":"①这一则是林彪亲笔写的，时间不详。","index":209,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6a155bfe35","type":"paragraph","text":"其十六①","index":210,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b1bae9a2b4","type":"paragraph","text":"亚里士多德《辩论的常识》（略）","index":211,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8d52d2226c","type":"paragraph","text":"［注］","index":212,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d57aadedef","type":"paragraph","text":"①这则笔记全录自亚里士多德《辩论常识篇》第八卷第七章“四种情况，四种回答”，笔者当年未抄录，今缺。","index":213,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b7aed7ad23","type":"paragraph","text":"其十七①","index":214,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3143e4d8fa","type":"paragraph","text":"3月13日","index":215,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"38543abc57","type":"paragraph","text":"中庸之道 亚里士多德合理我们注意：","index":216,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"90eae9240b","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）站在左的方面","index":217,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e5ba5cd3c0","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）大胆反极左思潮","index":218,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"14eec5a05d","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）坚反右倾（后退的）","index":219,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e2352fc79a","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）团结大多数立场模糊、认识错误的。","index":220,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"719a4d38ca","type":"paragraph","text":"（5）瓦解间接同盟军","index":221,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aacfb0c034","type":"paragraph","text":"（6）韬晦","index":222,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fb1cccb552","type":"paragraph","text":"曹操论英雄：胸有大志腹有良谋","index":223,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a1beef7311","type":"paragraph","text":"范","index":224,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3346596818","type":"paragraph","text":"［注］","index":225,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aa7c63dfeb","type":"paragraph","text":"①这是叶群记录的林彪谈话。要点据原编者说明，收在《一○一笔记》中。时间约为70年代初。","index":226,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b6bbed982f","type":"paragraph","text":"其十八①","index":227,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0db7487828","type":"paragraph","text":"两个决心","index":228,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c99c8b05a2","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）对一○一，表面一套不改。他对一号的，对自己全适用。","index":229,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a2f4c004b9","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）阳奉阴违——暗中写暗中做——表面应付。","index":230,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c7c174b460","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）先对他表风度：（1）一切是非，不说，不解释，只附和。（2）未成熟的话不说（自己想，练习默）。（3）把自己兴趣热情全隐，使他摸不住。（4）当他是外人，是贼骨头，勿示以感情。","index":231,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0b363dda17","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）吸收他的智慧。","index":232,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2266858fe2","type":"paragraph","text":"脑力劳动。","index":233,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f8a2bed220","type":"paragraph","text":"同学、同宿舍、同课堂、同事、同谋，而非同心。这样作最坏打算，自己永保精神准备，至少不会疯，不会上感。一○一他经常表示对我的不满、轻蔑，使我尝到被鞭打、被刺讽的痛楚，使我在行尸走肉般的生活中清醒过来。","index":234,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b6c81e50df","type":"paragraph","text":"但我怎么办？","index":235,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9c23214249","type":"paragraph","text":"工作——看不到成绩，依傍着人，被讽刺，被歧视。","index":236,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c25a5fb85b","type":"paragraph","text":"生活——照这轨道下去是无风度，是太无聊。但另外的也没有什么办法打开局面。","index":237,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6244b486eb","type":"paragraph","text":"学习——有收获，但不能一天到晚学而无所用。各项目帮助学了，再无项目。","index":238,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4bdca71ef6","type":"paragraph","text":"情感——根本谈不到。与一个专门仇恨的人，轻视人（轻视友情、子女、父兄——无意趣）、把人想得最坏、最无情、终日计算利害、专好推过于人们的人，勾心斗角、互相倾轧的人，何情可言！","index":239,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"258af76282","type":"paragraph","text":"虽然身体不好，但还有残余的精力。虽然看透了一切，但还有热情。怎能由男人把自己变成幽灵一样毫无作为的人！我将怎样打发日子，排遣精力？","index":240,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6217258469","type":"paragraph","text":"光念书，越呆越无用。光沉默，会疯。我想写。（1）写自己最熟悉的（还有得可写）。（2）写可少与人来往，少与一○一谈（保持自己一点天地）。（3）我有时间（虽对方不让写，可以隐写）。（4）我有条件请教人（问历史，吕某；问文艺，郭某）。（5）劳逸结合，注意身体。（6）应付其他，把精力用在一点上。","index":241,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"01968a04e4","type":"paragraph","text":"本是一把利刃，几十年被蒙住了尘埃。要扫掉尘土，跳出匣子，把往日受的侮辱变成力量。虽是后期，仍可放光。环境越恶劣，鞭打越残酷，越要有股横劲。自今日始，每日执笔，先写再说。哪怕无成就，至少可以打发时间、热情。哪怕累、疲劳，至少可免受气、发疯的结局。","index":242,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6d1a55b714","type":"paragraph","text":"让我用写来逃避现实吧！让我用写来寄托希望吧！让我用写来斩断痛苦的回忆和生活的过错吧！（几十年的时间，由人拨弄，任人歧视，这是多大的过错呀）。","index":243,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3ea483e484","type":"paragraph","text":"要收集语汇，围绕着“写”来生活（为写而休息才有意义，才不荒唐）。要读书（边读边写而相得益彰）。","index":244,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5522c9855f","type":"paragraph","text":"要与一○一谈话（有的放矢，吸收营养）。","index":245,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"53ac30b64b","type":"paragraph","text":"不怕无成就。不怕犯错（不犯立场错）。夺彩②（使无懈可击）自今日始。","index":246,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5d99d2b6da","type":"paragraph","text":" \t1961年11月24日","index":247,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bb256f942f","type":"paragraph","text":" \t于家乡福州，血的教之后","index":248,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b8a1ee6690","type":"paragraph","text":"（叶群的手印）","index":249,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e3b1413059","type":"paragraph","text":"［注］","index":250,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9ae601f333","type":"paragraph","text":"①这篇《两个决心》是叶群亲笔写的。","index":251,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4b233b3a66","type":"paragraph","text":"②“夺彩”，意谓放射夺目的光彩。","index":252,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e047fc33c3","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：香港《明报》月刊， 1994年3月号。","index":253,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bc33879e46","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}